{"tid":508191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅葉指數轉A級「極紅」 大棠一片紅過聖誕","createTime":"2017-12-24T04:10:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T06:48:19.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"65a2748a1e2408fb5bcb3fef951bb51fc7c9177c","tid":508191,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T04:10:19.000Z","msg":"今天平安夜，晚上節目多蘿蘿，日間不少人臨急選購聖誕禮物，商場勢必人頭湧湧，郊外亦不例外。元朗大欖郊野公園的紅葉指數已轉為A級「極紅」，齊齊「執葉」打卡自拍迎聖誕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n漁農自然護理署的「紅葉情報（2017-18）」網站在前日，即周五更新，指大欖郊野公園大棠山道的楓香林，已由B級的「開始變紅」，變成「B to A」，主要觀賞的品種有楓香、大頭茶、紅花荷。天氣愈冷，樹葉越變紅，主因是寒冷和強光照射下，致葉綠素加速分解，葉中的紅色素因此慢慢取而代之，由綠轉為黃及紅。據近年經驗，大棠紅葉的「極紅期」一般在12月尾至翌年1月上旬。<br />\n漁護署本月3日起至明年1月7日，逢星期日及公眾假期，在大欖郊野公園大棠舉辦紅葉導賞等活動，時間為上午10時30分至下午4時，市民可即場參加，額滿即止，費用全免。交通方面，漁護署建議郊遊人士可於元朗乘K66號巴士或紅色小巴，由大棠山路路口巴士站沿車路，步行上山約60分鐘到達楓香林。漁護署同時提醒，警方逢周六日及公眾假期會視乎人流，或會有封路或改道等措施，建議市民盡量使用公共交通工具前往。<br />\n紅葉情報（2017-18）網站：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.natureintouch.go\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.natureintouch.go&d=aWOvBEzwURDPjj9LZm7f9Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=3528b9ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.natureintouch.go</a>......oor/activity/nit_2011/0/759  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171224/large/1514082679_0585.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171224%2Flarge%2F1514082679_0585.jpg&h=bea97209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上周元朗大欖郊野公園的紅葉指數只達B級，但已人頭湧湧。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171224/57620790\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171224%2F57620790&d=aWOvBEzwURDPjj9LZm7f9Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=556bc738\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171224%2F57620790&h=e2bcc026\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171224/57620790</a>"},{"pid":"116797139c08b8c92034846813a584badd67d1f8","tid":508191,"uid":8048,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T04:12:02.000Z","msg":"無啦無啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b35e1cf2bd5949c897b985f1929fb4e04d1d8d","tid":508191,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無啦無啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n實迫到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a7624e6feb7f431d582d949310eb23b8271fa8","tid":508191,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T04:13:11.000Z","msg":"多人過倒數"},{"pid":"c14a57e0e7794b507538ca9083513499de6ab50c","tid":508191,"uid":131064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T04:16:02.000Z","msg":"傻閪先去"},{"pid":"c3bbc950cb013a3abc3f2dd4dee11be867f87c90","tid":508191,"uid":1171,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T04:16:39.000Z","msg":"上星期四去左，當時只係B級<br />\n人流就唔多，但星期六日應該多到喊<br />\n如果想去既巴打，<br />\n可以去元朗千色搭小巴<br />\n或者去朗屏坐K66<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/121417_3e91d7f8ee23c55d9475bba723aaa9c0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F121417_3e91d7f8ee23c55d9475bba723aaa9c0.jpeg&h=b74fd1ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/121439_29c58d58b82d95bb8d15de95392a24f3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F121439_29c58d58b82d95bb8d15de95392a24f3.jpeg&h=86a04167&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07b65c1d4f2d763cd90cb7e4de9734124dacfeda","tid":508191,"uid":131064,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T04:22:12.000Z","msg":"上IG S